overview:
LogiMindz is a technology solution provider helping you to attract, retain and service your customers better and in the process developing your business. Combining the deep technical expertise and understanding of business process with the advantage of its dual shore business model, LogiMindz helps you to unlock the potential of scattered and unrelated data & processes through integration and analysis.

Our goal is to understand your business, share a common business goal with you, and help you reach and exceed your objectives. We value the long-term relationship that we create with our customers and ultimately become an extension of their businesses.

We Deliver End-to-End solutions through valuable strategy development, consulting services, and highly skilled engineering execution. With a history of on-time/within-budget delivery, LogiMindz has built strong practices and worldwideDelivery capabilities in Custom Application Development , Product Engineering ,CRM, Enterprise Integration, and business intelligence.
